<h1>Reminder: Your Appointment is Tomorrow</h1>

<p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

<p>
    This is a friendly reminder that you have an appointment scheduled with us tomorrow.
</p>

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #dbeafe; border-left-color: #3b82f6;">
    <h3>Appointment Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{formatDate startTime "long"}} at {{formatDate startTime "time"}}</p>
    <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</p>
    <p><strong>Title:</strong> {{appointmentTitle}}</p>
</div>

{{#if meetingLink}}
<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Join Meeting</h3>
    <p>
        You can join the meeting using the link below. We recommend joining 5 minutes early to test your connection.
    </p>
    {{> button text="Join Meeting" url=meetingLink}}
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 16px;">
        <strong>Meeting Link:</strong><br>
        <a href="{{meetingLink}}" style="color: #3b82f6; word-break: break-all;">{{meetingLink}}</a>
    </p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<h2>Preparation Checklist</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Review your quote details before the meeting</li>
    <li>Prepare any questions you have for our team</li>
    <li>Ensure your device and internet connection are working properly</li>
    <li>Have a quiet space ready for the meeting</li>
</ul>

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left-color: #f59e0b;">
    <h3>Need to Reschedule?</h3>
    <p>
        If you need to reschedule or cancel, please contact us as soon as possible:
        <br>
        Phone: <strong>{{organizationPhone}}</strong>
        <br>
        Email: <strong>{{organizationEmail}}</strong>
    </p>
</div>

<p>
    We're looking forward to meeting with you!
</p>

<p>
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The {{organizationName}} Team</strong>
</p>